drop table "CON_PrintTemplate" cascade constraints;

/* Table: "CON_PrintTemplate" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_PrintTemplate"
(
"PrintTemplateID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"PrintTempCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"PrintTempName" NVARCHAR2(50) not null,
"PrintTempFile" NVARCHAR2(50) not null,
"TCPrintTempFile" NVARCHAR2(50),
"PrintADTempFile" NVARCHAR2(50),
"DiscountTempFile" NVARCHAR2(50),
"CreateDate" TIMESTAMP not null,
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"Remark" NVARCHAR2(200),
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreatetTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_CON_PRINTTEMPLATE primary key ("PrintTemplateID")
);

comment on column "CON_PrintTemplate"."PrintTempFile" is
'word宏文件';

comment on column "CON_PrintTemplate"."Enable" is
'1:有效 0：无效';
